**CVAT Dashboard Installation Guide**

- Create a new project from your onepanel dashboard.

Clone Onepanel demo project for cvat-dashboard   [**https://github.com/onepanelio/demos.git**](https://github.com/onepanelio/demos.git)

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

Select CVAT as your environment (it has nodered and jupyter also installed).

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

Select Storage and CLick on Create.

-
Next, Go to your workspace, and open terminal from the button in bottom right corner.









Install the dependencies using the following commands :

-
  -
pip install json2html ![](data:image/*;base64,)
  - npm install node-red-contrib-pythonshell
  - npm install node-red-contrib-queue-gate
  - npm install node-red-contrib-tableify
  - npm install node-red-dashboard

Authorize swagger API,

Go to this link :

        [https://c.onepanel.io/](https://c.onepanel.io/onepanel-demo/projects/cvat-dashboard/workspaces/notebook/label/api/swagger/)[**username**](https://c.onepanel.io/onepanel-demo/projects/cvat-dashboard/workspaces/notebook/label/api/swagger/)[/projects/](https://c.onepanel.io/onepanel-demo/projects/cvat-dashboard/workspaces/notebook/label/api/swagger/)[**your\_project\_name**](https://c.onepanel.io/onepanel-demo/projects/cvat-dashboard/workspaces/notebook/label/api/swagger/)[/workspaces/](https://c.onepanel.io/onepanel-demo/projects/cvat-dashboard/workspaces/notebook/label/api/swagger/)[**your\_workspace\_name**](https://c.onepanel.io/onepanel-demo/projects/cvat-dashboard/workspaces/notebook/label/api/swagger/)[/label/api/swagger/](https://c.onepanel.io/onepanel-demo/projects/cvat-dashboard/workspaces/notebook/label/api/swagger/)

And click on authorize, and enter these credentials.

Username : admin

Password : password

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)











 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

Next, Import the Dashboard Flow Json file to your Nodered Panel, ([https://github.com/onepanelio/demos/blob/master/cvat\_dashboard/flows.json](https://github.com/onepanelio/demos/blob/master/cvat_dashboard/flows.json))

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

Click on the Deploy Button :

The dashboard is live at :
